Package: hexwall
Title: Create Hexagon Tile Patterns with HTML
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", , "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An htmltools extension for creating hexagonal tile patterns using hex.css styling. 
    Supports automatic logo detection from installed packages and custom image paths.
    Images are embedded as base64 data URIs for completely self-contained HTML output.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
